The board of Kogi State Internal Revenue Service (KGIRS) has been sacked with immediate effect, The Nation has learnt. An impeccable source said the cleanout was carried out on Monday following summon of the erstwhile chairman to the Government House. The source confided in The Nation the development caught everyone unawares. The source stated the board chairman and directors were told to vacate offices within 10 minutes by a Government delegation that followed the former chairman to the office. Details shortlyâ€¦